I0306 23:04:27.824706   12160 conn_opt.go:53] jsonrpc2: --> notif: textDocument/didOpen: {"textDocument":{"uri":"file:///home/azehagowa/README.md","languageId":"markdown","version":1,"text":"#Azehagowa\n\nAzehagowa is a lightweight project repository maintained by azehagowa-creator.\nThis package is designed to provide a clean, minimal, and extendable foundation for Node.js-based applications.\n\n\n---\n\n🚀 Installation\n\nClone the repository:\n\ngit clone https://github.com/azehagowa-creator/Azehagowa.git\ncd Azehagowa\n\nInstall dependencies:\n\nnpm install\n\n\n---\n\n▶️ Usage\n\nStart the project:\n\nnpm start\n\nOr run directly:\n\nnode index.js\n\n\n---\n\n📦 Project Structure\n\nAzehagowa/\n│── index.js\n│── package.json\n│── README.md\n\n\n---\n\n🛠 Requirements\n\nNode.js (v18+ recommended)\n\nnpm\n\n\n\n---\n\n📄 License\n\nLicensed under Apache-2.0.\n\n\n---\n\n👤 Author\n\nelparadiso\n\n\n---\n"}}
